NAME
    Tie::Handle::LogGer - Filehandle to log to Log::ger

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of Tie::Handle::LogGer (from Perl
    distribution Tie-Handle-LogGer), released on 2017-08-08.

SYNOPSIS
     use Tie::Handle::LogGer;
     tie *FH, 'Tie::Handle::LogGer',
         level => 'debug',       # optional, default is 'warn'
         category => 'Foo::Bar', # optional, default is current package
     ;

     print FH "this is a debug log message";
     print FH "this is another debug log message, data=%s", $data;

DESCRIPTION
    This module ties a filehandle to Log::ger logger object. For sure a
    silly module, just a proof of concept.

METHODS
  TIEHANDLE classname, list
  PRINT list
HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Tie-Handle-LogGer>.

